'''汝陽龍屬'''（[[屬|屬]]名：{{lang|la|''Ruyangosaurus''}}，意為「[[汝陽|汝陽]]蜥蜴」）是[[蜥腳類|蜥腳類]][[恐龍|恐龍]]的一個[[屬|屬]]，屬於巨型的[[巨龍形類|巨龍形類]]，生存於[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]前期（約1億2500萬至1億年前<ref name = XuL2012>{{ cite journal | author = 徐莉, 潘泽成, 王志宏, 张兴辽, 贾松海, 吕君昌, 姜宝良 | title = 河南省汝阳盆地白垩系的发现及意义 | journal = 地质论评 | volume = 58 | issue = 4 | year = 2012 | pages = 601–613 | issn = 0371-5736 | doi = 10.3969/j.issn.0371-5736.2012.04.001 | url = http://www.geojournals.cn/georeven/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20125804001&year_id=2012&quarter_id=4&falg=1 }}</ref>）的[[東亞|東亞]]。化石發現於[[中國|中國]][[河南省|河南省]][[汝陽縣|汝陽縣]]的[[郝嶺組|郝嶺組]]地層，和[[黃河巨龍|黃河巨龍]]、[[峴山龍|峴山龍]]與{{link-en|雲夢龍屬|Yunmenglong|雲夢龍}}<ref name = Lu2013>{{ cite journal | author = Lü, J.; Xu, L.; Pu, H.; Zhang, X.; Zhang, Y.; Jia, S.; Chang, H.; Zhang, J.; Wei, X. | title = A new sauropod dinosaur (Dinosauria, Sauropoda) from the late Early Cretaceous of the Ruyang Basin (central China) | journal = Cretaceous Research | volume = 44 | year = 2013 | pages = 202–213 | issn = 0371-5736 | doi = 10.1016/j.cretres.2013.04.009 | url = }}</ref>同屬於白堊紀[[洛陽盆地|洛陽盆地]]的蜥腳類動物群，因而得名<ref name = Lu2009>{{cite journal | author = 吕君昌, 徐莉, 贾松海, 张兴辽, 张纪明, 杨丽丽, 尤海鲁, 季强 | title = 记河南汝阳白垩纪一新的巨型蜥脚类恐龙 <small>[A new gigantic sauropod dinosaur from the Cretaceous of Ruyang, Henan, China]</small> | journal = 地质通报 | volume = 28 | issue = 1 | year = 2009 | pages = 1–10 | issn = 1671-2552 | doi = 10.3969/j.issn.1671-2552.2009.01.001 | url = http://dzhtb.cgs.cn/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20090101&flag=&journal_id=gbc&year_id=2009 | access-date = 2019-07-18 | archive-date = 2017-09-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170926235308/http://dzhtb.cgs.cn/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20090101&flag=&journal_id=gbc&year_id=2009 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = XuL2010>{{ cite journal | author = 徐丽, 张兴辽, 吕君昌, 贾松海, 潘泽成, 秦爽, 朱红卫, 曾光艳 | title = 河南省汝阳巨型蜥脚类恐龙动物群及含化石地层时代讨论 | journal = 地质论评 | volume = 56 | issue = 6 | year = 2010 | pages = 761–768 | issn = 0371-5736 | url = http://www.geojournals.cn/georev/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20100106001&flag=&journal_id=georev&year_id=2010 }}</ref>。

就軀體比例而言，汝陽龍具有特長的頸部，依據現有[[頸椎|頸椎]]化石的頸部重建長度可達 15.5 公尺，在所有恐龍中僅次於[[中加馬門溪龍|中加馬門溪龍]]。保守估計汝陽龍的已知最小個體全長至少有 28 公尺，而大部分復原版本的全長皆可超過 30 公尺，體重逾 50 噸<ref name=Pu2016>{{cite book | author = 蒲含勇, 吕君昌, 梁小菊, 徐莉, 杨杨, 高殿松, 常华丽, 单昌昊 | title = 河南古生物图鉴 | publisher = 地质出版社 | isbn = 978-7-116-08223-6 | date = 2016年3月 | page = 30–37 }}</ref><ref name=Paul2016>{{cite book | author = Paul, G. S. | title = The Princeton Field Guide to Dinosaurs: Second Edition | publisher = Princeton University Press | isbn = 978-0-691-16766-4 | date = 2016年11月 | page = 207, 231 }}</ref>，體型很可能超越{{link-en|新疆巨龍屬|Xinjiangtitan|新疆巨龍}}與[[馬門溪龍|馬門溪龍]]，或與這兩者持平，是[[亞洲|亞洲]]最大型的恐龍之一<ref name = Lu2009/><ref name = Wu>{{cite journal | author = 吴文昊, 周长付, Oliver Wings, 关谷透, 董枝明 | title = 新疆鄯善中侏罗世巨型蜥脚类恐龙的发现 | journal = 世界地质 | volume = 32 | issue = 2 | year = 2013 | pages = 437–446 | issn = 1004-5589 | doi = 10.3969/j.issn.1004-5589.2013.03.002 | url = http://www.dinosaurhunter.org/files/globalgeol.-2013-wu_et_al-sauropod_xinjiangtitan__turpan_basin__china.pdf | access-date = 2019-07-18 | archive-date = 2013-11-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131110174159/http://www.dinosaurhunter.org/files/globalgeol.-2013-wu_et_al-sauropod_xinjiangtitan__turpan_basin__china.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

